      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for CFD simulation must comply with documented QA procedures including version control, regression testing, and release validation at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "SQA documentation exists but regression test suite covers only 72% of solver modules. Version control is enforced; however, formal release validation records are incomplete for the turbulence sub-model used in hemolysis prediction. Achieved level falls one gradation below required."
