      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal order-of-accuracy studies and manufactured-solution benchmarks required for all active numerical schemes at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy studies were completed for the primary Navier-Stokes solver using the method of manufactured solutions. The hemolysis scalar transport sub-model was verified only through comparison to published benchmarks, not through formal MMS testing, limiting achieved level to 3."
