      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence error, round-off error, and solver residual behavior must be formally characterized and shown to be negligible relative to discretization error.",
      "rationale": "Solver residuals were monitored to 10^-5 for continuity and momentum equations. Formal characterization of iterative convergence error and round-off error was not performed. This factor is flagged as an epistemic gap at MRL 5; achieved level defaults to 1."
    },
