      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed propagating uncertainty in fluid viscosity, density, and hemolysis model constants (alpha, beta, C) using literature-derived distributions. Rotational speed uncertainty was not included in the UQ sweep. Input traceability to primary measurement data is partial; some distributions rely on secondary literature sources without original measurement uncertainty."
