    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction is accepted for documentation purposes despite multiple credibility factor gaps. All 13 ASME V&V 40 factors have been evaluated; 7 factors were formally assessed (all with achieved levels below required levels at MRL 5) and 6 factors remain as epistemic gaps. The ContextOfUse is well-described in prose, referencing 5 flow-speed operating conditions and Monte Carlo UQ requirements. The assessment is accepted as a complete gap analysis record to inform future V&V activities, not as evidence of model adequacy for regulatory submission.",
